Package: globalClimData
Title: Package to Download and process Climate data based on global or country specific or bounding box.
Version: 2.0.0
Before: Version:  1.1.9
After: Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sushil", "Paudel", , "spaudel@clarku.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package helps to Download and process TerraClimate data based on global or country specific or bounding box. 
                You can use TerraClimate and WorldClim data, and gridMET data as a source. 
                The package provides functions to download climate data for various variables such as 
                temperature, precipitation, and others, and process them for any analysis or modeling purpose. 
                The package also provides functions to extract climate data for specific locations and time periods.
